Required Options.
--bmk <path-to-executable>           Path to the benchmark executable binary.
Optional:
--help                               Print this help message
-O0                                  Optimization Level 0 (single-cycle processor)
-O1                                  Optimization Level 1 (pipelined processor)
-O2                                  Optimization Level 2 (custom optimization TBD; includes O1)
-O3                                  Optimization Level 3 (custom optimization TBD; includes O2)
-O4                                  Optimization Level 4 (custom optimization TBD; includes O3)
                                     Defaults to -O0
